snippet.title: Strange Foreign Games | Russian Roulette 1 [DOS](1996)
snippet.description: a awful clone of Terminal Velocity... with horrible difficulty scaling to hide its short length ... and that's all i can say about this Russian Production ... also played part 2 that wanted to be a FPS exploration game like Fallout ... a game way ahead of its time ... but this game, skip it
